name: Warmup_Div01_Sub01
queryText:
SELECT DISTINCT
GmailD1S1.CPF,
GmailD1S1.NOME,
GmailD1S1.EMAIL,
GmailD1S1.EMAIL_VALIDO,
CASE

  WHEN CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD1S1.NOME) = 0 THEN GmailD1S1.NOME

  ELSE SUBSTRING( GmailD1S1.NOME , 1, CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD1S1.NOME) )

END AS PNOME
FROM Gmail_DIV01_SUB01 GmailD1S1
UNION
